resources.string: This app is created to be a fun way to learn more about Taylor Swift and her music! Taylor is a 12 time grammy award, 14 time VMA award, 29 time Bilboard Award, and 23 time American Music Award winner. Aside from being a music icon, she is also a philanthropest, smart buissinesswoman, and an inspiration to girls and women around the world!
Taylor grew up on a christmas tree farm!
Taylors mom wanted her to be a horseback rider
Taylor wrote a 350-page novel when she was 12, which has never been published.
Taylor wrote every song by herself on her third album, "Speak Now."

Hi! Im Rose Peters, the creator of this app and a lifelong swiftie. I have listened to her music ever since I was little. I am also inspired by her as a person. To me, she demonstrates confidence, resilience, and originality. I think that her work can inspire many others as well. I created this app to honor her! Let me know what you think about it!
